, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事情我都聽說了，那些人別想就這麼抓到你！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你別害怕，跟我走就好，我們都會幫你——", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？不......我沒有害怕！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 8.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊蒙德，你先鬆手......你誤會了！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#10$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#10$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "jump", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "power": 5.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 8.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉！是我太著急了......很疼嗎？", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事的。", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽我說，萊蒙德！我是、我是自願跟他們去拉特蘭的！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼......？", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#6$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說胡話了！他們拿什麼威脅你了？你去那裡會死的！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那也是我罪有應得！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別管我了，萊蒙德，沒有人強迫我也沒有人威脅我，是我害了菲娜，我不能就這麼逃走！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德爾菲娜......那是個意外......", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#3$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不！我不想連你也說什麼“那是個意外”！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "意外......意外！是啊，我怎麼可能會故意拿銃對著菲娜，那只是個可悲的意外......但是菲娜真的死了！死了！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊蒙德，菲娜不會再睜開眼睛，不會再和我們說話了！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "福爾圖娜，冷靜......別這樣抓，別傷到你自己！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#11$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想冷靜下來的......我也不想這樣又哭又叫！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#6$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是為什麼沒有人因此責備我？！為什麼所有人都說只是個意外，好像菲娜她的死用一個輕飄飄的“意外”就可以一筆帶過一樣？！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$2"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菲娜她、她被我殺死了！是不是意外有區別嗎？！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#6$2"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......喘氣，別憋著。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#11$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#2$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......哈......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#2$2"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好點了？", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#1$2"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，我不該這樣......但是萊蒙德，我不知道該怎麼辦才好......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只知道......我不能走，不能逃，不能當作什麼都沒有發生，不能真的認可那是個意外。", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是我的罪......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#5$2"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說了。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#11$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你別擔心我，萊蒙德，或許也沒有那麼糟......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯普莉雅，就是今天來的那位拉特蘭的使者小姐，她對我很好，我沒有吃什麼苦頭。", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許回到拉特蘭後他們會把我關起來？", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我長出了角......我也不知道現在我還算不算是薩科塔，不過，就算不是也沒什麼......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，我沒事的，萊蒙德，你——", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行。", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes"