ontent": "策反談不上，他就是那種人，只做對自己有利的事。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在自保這方面，他比我還有本事......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總覺得好像有人在盯著我看......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，奧倫你是終於多疑到出現幻覺了嗎？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起幻覺，我更願意相信是真的有什麼人躲在角落裡偷聽。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#8$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，別那樣看我，開個玩笑而已。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，你看著的那個墮天使小姑娘呢？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......她啊，應該已經乖乖睡著了吧。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別扯了，說回正題。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛剛說計劃提前？可以是可以，不過這可和說好的不一樣。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#8$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼突然修改計劃？給我一個理由。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#8$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對你來說沒什麼區別不是嗎？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是沒什麼區別，所以我也可以選擇不合作囉。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......如果我沒記錯，這次的調動權在我，斯普莉雅。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以回去寫檢討。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好像有點急躁，奧倫。到底怎麼了？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次本來就不是擺在台面上的行動，如果不是教宗閣下忽然被什麼聖徒的事情吸引了注意，要調動部隊可沒有那麼容易。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算是這樣，教宗閣下似乎還是察覺到了什麼，還特地派了費德里科......嘖，想要瞞住費德里科那傢伙有多難你不會不知道。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真覺得自己瞞住了？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大機率沒有。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我也算是摸清楚他的性子了，只要他不深究，就問題不大。反正我們的目的只是攔截所有想離開的人不是嗎。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反而是你，奧倫，一旦你下令讓部隊動手，這事可就真的瞞不住了。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#8$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科不是會在意手段的人。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可不好說。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提前申明，他要是想對你動手，我沒這個本事攔住他。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是可悲的同事情誼......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰會在這時候聯絡我......呃。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#2$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你自己看。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "立刻把奧倫帶到入口大廳來。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "——費德里科", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來是完全沒瞞住。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#12$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#5$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說的那些我自會處理，斯普莉雅，現在按我說的去做。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓能行動的部隊都過來，立刻由我們的人接管整座修道院。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......真有這麼急？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個和修道院同生共死六十年的老人，為了那些薩卡茲一意孤行，甚至能做出扣押拉特蘭使者這種事。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他被逼到絕路，卻忽然鬆口，還提出要做“最後的道別”如此有儀式感的事......你覺得會是因為什麼？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再加上一群有點來頭的薩卡茲，還有隱身在暗處的幾位“客人”......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的動作要快。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我總有種不好的預感......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#6$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#4$2", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#7$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#4$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接管......？什麼意思......為什麼......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#4$2"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_931_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還不明白嗎？！那個薩科塔一直都在騙我們！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我得去告訴杰拉爾德老大！我就知道！那些拉特蘭人從一開始就沒安好心......！", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "福爾圖娜，現在和我一起反而會有危險，你找一個安全的地方等我，他們應該不會立刻對你動手——", "name": "萊蒙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_931_1#7$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下，萊蒙德！", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#10$2"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_927_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......呼......", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#1$2"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我改變主意了。我要和你一起去。", "name": "福爾圖娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_927_1#1$2"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g1_monasteryentrance", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好巧啊，兩位。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安女士，太好了，你安然無恙。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼收穫嗎？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_electrcwhlchrrll", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看起來有些憂慮，執行者里凱萊。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#9$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在追查一件我有點在意的事，和那位主教閣下有關，但......嗯，總之還需要繼續調查。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢，費德里科，你在做什麼？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工作。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，我當然知道你是在工作......你發現什麼了？是不是和薩卡茲有關？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說晚上的那場火災是薩卡茲那邊有人心生不滿，故意放火，這是真的嗎？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是什麼新式的娛樂節目嗎？你們的即興相聲表演？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#9$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玩笑到此為止。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玩笑？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#5$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫和斯普莉雅很快會過來會合。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，這個口氣......費德里科，你從一開始就知道奧倫是故意躲起來的？", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#8$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "顯而易見。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他真不走運，前不久萬國峰會的時候才和你對上，這次偏偏又碰上你。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，之前奧倫按照自己的判斷私自行動，我也是默許的。畢竟安布羅修修道院的情況這麼複雜，不留一點後手可不行。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我總覺得他現在需要一點點提醒......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人聯繫我說要立刻趕到，還讓我捎上奧倫，到底出了什麼急事？", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？奧倫，你終於肯乖乖露面啦。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，好久不見啊，蕾繆安。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這不是在合作完成任務嘛，別說得這麼生分......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正因為是合作夥伴，所以現在你還可以站在這裡說話哦。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管你有什麼樣的計劃......你那種強硬的做法不太適合現在的修道院，差不多該停手了，奧倫。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，你和費德里科就不能學學旁邊那位，假裝什麼都不知情嗎？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能別拉我下水嗎......", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "里凱萊的問題在回到公證所後自然會清算。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_372_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我謝謝你，奧倫。", "name": "里凱萊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_372_1#6$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於你，奧倫。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你確實判斷有單獨行動的必要，可以嘗試說服我。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這裡沒有其他人了，我就直說吧。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯普莉雅，你難道真以為我沒發現你偷偷摸摸想放走那兩個年輕人？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個墮天的薩科塔和一個薩卡茲，他們顯眼得讓我想假裝看不見都難啊。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4015_spuria_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嘖。", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#8$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這傢伙......", "name": "斯普莉雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_4015_spuria_1#8$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坦白說，我早就有點不耐煩這種磨磨蹭蹭的感覺了。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來你是在指責我的做法？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#6$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不敢。不敢。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，我也有我的做法。我們已經在這裡耗掉了不少時間，總該考慮考慮，怎麼才能儘快完成工作，還不出任何紕漏吧？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說的做法就是私自調動特勤部隊？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說得好像這很輕易一樣嘛。你知道的，“調動部隊”和“下令行動”是兩回事。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了能有一個合適的、妥當的、教宗閣下也無法反對的行動理由，我可是苦惱了好一陣子啊。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在正好，現成的藉口送上門來了——", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個薩卡茲小子，是叫萊蒙德吧？燒毀聖堂可是大罪，更遑論他還是個薩卡茲，我們接手後不論是扣押還是展開後續調查，都不過分吧？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "燒毀聖堂的犯人不是他，你所謂的理由並不成立。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我查清真相之前，不需要你的隊伍介入。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真相，哈，真相如何真的那麼重要嗎？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們的人接管這裡，把一切都安排妥帖，這難道不是最高效、最合理的做法？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科，你難道沒有這麼考慮過？你真有這麼看重真相？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#7$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫，你這樣做，難道就不怕這裡的居民反抗？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_925_1#7$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安，我以為你不會說這樣的傻話。如果有薩卡茲要反抗......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不是更理想了嗎？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰在外面！", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_door", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叩門聲在陡然安靜下來的大廳中迴響。"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "門扉發出令人牙酸的吱呀響聲，室外異常明亮的月光透過打開的門縫安靜地灑入。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人獨自站在一線月光中。"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科先生......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "39_i06", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.15, "yScaleFrom": 1.15, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克萊芒？", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......終於找到你了，費德里科先生。", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人，托我把“這個”轉交給您......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰委託你？這是——", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "未出口的話音在空氣中戛然而止。"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "背著光的人影緩慢地走近，瘦高的男人始終低低地垂著頭。"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整間屋子的光此時好像都聚集於他一人，可過於刺眼的光亮，又反在人的身上抹出濃重駭人的陰影。"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科終於看清對方手上捧著的東西。"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那據說是旁人托克萊芒轉交給他的東西。"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一把匕首。"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳舊但鋒利，曾被藏於某人的身後。"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在匕首旁......"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那用布包裹著，下方被染成紅色，還有液體不斷溢出的東西。"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那是什麼？"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是......"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......“罪人”霍斯特·蒂芬達爾自願獻上的頭顱。", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“罪人”已承認所有惡事都是其一人所為，所有罪名，都由其一人承擔。", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今首惡伏誅，剩下的只是一群流民，不足掛齒......", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望......希望拉特蘭的各位使者，能夠就此手下留情，不再繼續追究。", "name": "克萊芒"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g1_monasteryentrance", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科先生，他、杰拉爾德他在臨走前要我對你說——", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他請求你，求你帶走通緝犯霍斯特的頭顱和武器......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放過福爾圖娜和萊蒙德......", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放過其他薩卡茲。", "name": "克萊芒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_924_1#5$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}